{
  "stem": "597.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I used to wear a-- a special-- a special dress, like a white dress on top-- you know, white.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And very, very-- very devoted to the Jewish religion-- very devoted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was raised up in this city-- in this place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'm, up to now, I'm-- I'm religious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I feel like to-- I believe in God-- that spared me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Even if I went through a lot, and I knew we went-- we went through a lot, and I didn't like it, the thing what I went through.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because I felt very guilty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's why I am a human being.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The same thing-- my friends-- and I cannot do the things what my friends-- gentile friends are doing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I'm not-- and I was-- and even sometimes I was thinking in my head that I would like to be born another animal, not a human being-- during the war.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because that this way-- that day, I couldn't understand this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I feel like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because-- because I was born Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I felt different-- and orthodox, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't eat all the food, what everybody was eating.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But during the war, I hide my-- we-- in the hiding place, I eat everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother told me, in a time like that, you-- you don't-- you don't have to be-- choose food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to eat whatever somebody gives you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's a-- it's a-- it's a war time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Eat everything.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I listened to my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I eat whatever my-- my-- I did what my mother told me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kabbalah Hasidism.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In this-- that-- that famous rabbi, Rabbi Pinchas Shapiro-- they called him Rabbi [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He spread all the Hasidism in Kabbalah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was spread all over around the-- in-- around the whole Poland in nearby neighborhoods.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
